{"tid":531780,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"青森八甲田山系樹冰遭塗鴉 疑是外國遊客所為","createTime":"2018-01-17T07:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T07:43:40.000Z","uid":164608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bdaa4790bed1f6fe3818c6cf4d511e5de63df0e3","tid":531780,"uid":164608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/154243_bcd8a7c6d7fb6e000e2523b77013d2b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F154243_bcd8a7c6d7fb6e000e2523b77013d2b3.png&h=d878756d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/154246_2090f344148f3fc287907b5c9f7d316d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F154246_2090f344148f3fc287907b5c9f7d316d.png&h=7a5d3a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n指定為十和田八幡平國立公園、位在青森市八甲田山系的樹冰，日前得知曾遭噴上粉紅色的螢光塗鴉。現場好幾棵樹冰以及周邊綿延約100平方公尺的積雪表面，以中英文噴上「生日快樂」等文字。<br />\n<br />\n　　現場位於八甲田纜車的山頂公園站周邊，海拔1324公尺，14日下午1點左右，纜車營運公司接獲滑雪客通報:「有男女在惡搞樹冰。」<br />\n<br />\n　　根據該公司表示，男女研判為外國遊客，並以中英日文對話，滑雪客雖當場勸阻，男女卻不收手。該公司員工當天花費約1小時清除塗鴉。<br />\n<br />\n班支那狗真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}